  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やはりそう簡単にはいかないか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just as I expected, this won't be so easy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>時を越える聖剣か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A holy sword tthat can pass through time...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんなものを手に入れて、
ヒューネガルドは何に使うつもりなんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What is Huegard planning on
doing with it if he gets ahold it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Revisiting later with context.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいや。
俺はリオンを信じてる。
話はあとでゆっくりと聞くよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine. I trust you.
Later on, we can take our time
and I can listen to your story then.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
